00:00:00.390 --> 00:00:03.210
Bu sinovda siz TextView ob’ektini 
yaratishni va unda metodlarni

00:00:03.210 --> 00:00:05.210
chaqirishni mashq qilasiz.

00:00:05.210 --> 00:00:06.930
Bu shunchaki mashq uchun bo‘lgani uchun,

00:00:06.930 --> 00:00:11.250
biz buni JustJava ilovasidan tashqarida 
yangi Android ilovasida yaratamiz.

00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:13.020
Bu orqali JustJava ilovasida 
tartibsizlik keltirib chiqarmaymiz.

00:00:14.370 --> 00:00:19.070
Android Studio-da quydagi &amp;gt; New Project 
fayliga o‘tib Wizard proyektini oching.

00:00:19.070 --> 00:00:21.650
Keyin bularning barchasi uchun default 
qiymatlarni qabul qilishingiz mumkin. 

00:00:21.650 --> 00:00:25.620
Bo‘sh faoliyat shablonini tanlaganingizga 
ishonch hosil qiling, so‘ngra "Finish" ni bosing.

00:00:28.210 --> 00:00:31.190
Loyihangiz yaratilgach, qurilmangizda 
ilovangizni ishga tushiring.

00:00:32.380 --> 00:00:36.220
default holatda "Hello World" 
so‘zi paydo bo‘lishi kerak. 

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:38.220
Ammo hozir biz biroz boshqacharoq 
narsani amalga oshiramiz. 

00:00:38.220 --> 00:00:42.340
MainActivity sinfida biz 
onCreate metodini o‘zgartiramiz. 

00:00:42.340 --> 00:00:46.600
Ushbu faoliyatning asosiy XML joylashuv 
taribida setContentView ni chaqirish o‘rniga

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:49.080
biz u yerda o‘zimizning TextView mizni 
yaratamiz va sozlaymiz. 

00:00:50.390 --> 00:00:51.960
Android yaratuvchilarining saytida, 

00:00:51.960 --> 00:00:56.010
o‘quv bo‘limi mavjud va u yerda birinchi 
ilovangizni qanday yaratish haqida so‘z ketadi. 

00:00:56.010 --> 00:00:59.600
Xususan, darslikning "Xabarlarni 
ko‘rsatish" bo‘limiga qarayman. 

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:02.220
Bu sizga onCreate 
metodida TextView yaratishingiz

00:01:02.220 --> 00:01:03.930
mumkinligini aytadi

00:01:03.930 --> 00:01:07.290
Va bu yerda bu darsda avvalroq
tanish bo‘lgan kod. 

00:01:07.290 --> 00:01:08.850
Biz yangi TextView ni yaratamiz va 

00:01:08.850 --> 00:01:11.720
uni textView deb nomlangan
o‘zgaruvchining ichida saqlaymiz. 

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:14.708
Bu konstruktor kirish parametri 
sifatida kontekstni talab qiladi. 

00:01:14.708 --> 00:01:18.140
Va biz (uni) kirish parametri 
sifatida o‘tkazmoqdamiz, 

00:01:18.140 --> 00:01:21.780
chunki (bu) joriy 
faoliyatga tegishlidir.

00:01:21.780 --> 00:01:24.450
Va faoliyat ham
kontekstdir, shuning uchun 

00:01:24.450 --> 00:01:27.530
u bizga TextView ob’ektini 
to‘g‘ri shaklda yaratib beradi. 

00:01:27.530 --> 00:01:30.610
So‘ngra biz TextView ob’ektida
metodlarni chaqirishimiz mumkin. 

00:01:30.610 --> 00:01:35.330
Esda saqlang, textView - bu, 
o‘zgaruvchining nomi, TextView sinfi emas.

00:01:35.330 --> 00:01:38.360
Shuning uchun u kichkina harfla yozilgan. 

00:01:38.360 --> 00:01:42.430
Biz misol sifatida textView.setTextSize 
va textView.setText ni chaqirishimiz mumin.

00:01:43.830 --> 00:01:47.160
Pastga tushamiz va bizga 
setContentView ni chaqirishni va

00:01:47.160 --> 00:01:49.890
uni textView ga kirish parametri sifatda 
o‘tkazishimiz mumkinligini aytmoqda.

00:01:49.890 --> 00:01:51.690
Agar yanayam pastroqqa tushsangiz,
u yerda sizga onCreate metodi 

00:01:51.690 --> 00:01:53.230
uchun kod namunasi mavjud. 

00:01:54.230 --> 00:01:55.520
Bizga bu qismi zarur emas.

00:01:55.520 --> 00:01:58.360
Biz faqatgina bu qismiga e’tibor qaratamiz, 
u yerda textView ni yaratamiz va 

00:01:58.360 --> 00:02:01.160
uni faoliyat contentView ning 
joylashuv tartibi sifatida sozlaymiz. 

00:02:02.440 --> 00:02:04.610
Orqaga qaytib, Android Studio-da 
MainActivity sinfida,

00:02:04.610 --> 00:02:07.030
men onCreate metodini o‘zgartirmoqchiman.

00:02:07.030 --> 00:02:08.394
Men bu yerda bir necha bo‘sh
qatorlarni kiritmoqchiman. 

00:02:09.535 --> 00:02:12.065
Birinchi, konstruktordan foydalanib 
yangi TextView ob’ektini yarataman. 

00:02:13.245 --> 00:02:15.535
Men o‘zgaruvchiga TextView 
nomini bermoqchiman, lekin 

00:02:15.535 --> 00:02:20.075
siz istagan nomingizni qo‘llashingiz
mumkin, toki u buning 

00:02:20.075 --> 00:02:21.075
nimaligini to‘g‘ri ifodalasin.

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.870
Siz yaratgan matn o‘ziga 
konteksni talab qiladi, shu sababli 

00:02:24.870 --> 00:02:28.100
men ushbu faoliyatga murojaat 
qilish uchun bu narsaga o‘tmoqchiman.

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:30.500
Va matnning keyingi qatorida, 

00:02:30.500 --> 00:02:32.630
textView ob’ektida metodni
chaqirmoqchiman. 

00:02:33.770 --> 00:02:38.100
Nuqatani bosishim bilan, u menga 
textView ob’ektida chaqirishim mumkin 

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.730
bo‘lgan barcha metodlarni ko‘rsatadi.

00:02:40.990 --> 00:02:44.340
Agar yozishni boshlasam, u menga avtomatik 
ravishda to‘ldiruvchi namunalarni taqdim qiladi.

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:47.720
Ko‘rishingiz mumkinki, variantlar qisqardi. 

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:51.230
Men ushbu avtomatik to‘ldirishni amalga 
oshirish uchun, setText ni tanlayman. 

00:02:53.140 --> 00:02:56.370
So‘ngra, kirish argumanti sifatda
men satr joylashim mumkin. 

00:02:56.370 --> 00:02:59.230
Va oxirga qadam, setContentView 
qatorini sozlashimiz kerak.

00:02:59.230 --> 00:03:04.240
Bu XML joylashuv tartibi faylidan 
foydalanish o‘rniga,shunchaki textView ga joylayman.

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:06.810
Uni saqlayman va uni 
qurilmada ishga tushiraman. 

00:03:07.860 --> 00:03:11.840
Men kutayotgan natijam, hozir ekranda 
"Hello World" so‘zining o‘rniga "Wow" 

00:03:11.840 --> 00:03:15.030
deydigan yangi textView ni ko‘rsatishi kerak. 

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:15.660
Va shunday qilyapti.

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:17.860
Garchan bu biroz qoniqarsiz.

00:03:17.860 --> 00:03:20.390
Shu sababli men uni biroz 
qiziqarli qilmoqchiman. 

00:03:20.390 --> 00:03:24.198
Men sizni ushbu textView ob’ektida
boshqa metodlar bilan ishlashingizni,

00:03:24.198 --> 00:03:27.254
masalan, rangini, matn o‘lchamini 
o‘zgartirishingizni istayman. 

00:03:27.254 --> 00:03:29.294
Agar siz yanada qiziquvchan bo‘lsangiz, 

00:03:29.294 --> 00:03:32.780
textView ob’ektida boshqa metodlarni
ham chaqirib ko‘rishingiz mumkin. 

00:03:32.780 --> 00:03:35.280
textView uchun online hujjatlarni ko‘rib chiqing.

00:03:35.280 --> 00:03:38.370
Yana qanday metodlardan foydalanishingiz
mumkinligini bilish uchun. 

00:03:38.370 --> 00:03:40.490
Tugatganingizdan so‘ng, davom
etish uchun ushbu qutilarga bosing. 

